    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest an increased focus on the Middle East and Central Command area of responsibility, particularly in relation to potential operations involving Iran. The deployment of USS Tripoli (LHA-7) and USS Gerald R. Ford to the region indicates heightened readiness for operations. Additionally, reports indicate ongoing efforts by U.S. forces to scale back barriers at testing ranges and create a new &#39;marketplace&#39; for medium unmanned surface vessels. These developments suggest a complex and dynamic military environment with multiple actors and interests.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
